These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: july, february, april, december, november, september, march
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: blues, classical, jazz, r&b, reggae, rock, soul
The people have 7 different jobs:  lawyer, scientist, project-manager, musician, dressmaker, social-worker, librarian
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left##1
 2. the scientist is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 3. the librarian is between the fan of classical and the fan of blues##2
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the social-worker##1
 5. the fan of classical is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is the librarian##1
 7. the fan of r&b is between the musician and the person who's birthday is in november##2
 8. the dressmaker is on the left of the social-worker##1
 9. the social-worker is on the left of the lawyer##1
10. the person who's birthday is in march is the fan of jazz##1
11. the fan of rock is the person who's birthday is in december##1
12. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
13. the lawyer is the fan of reggae##1
14. the person who's birthday is in september is between the project-manager and the librarian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Birthday   | november | july     | september | february | december | march  | april  |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | r&b        | classical  | soul     | rock   | jazz       | reggae   |
| Job         | scientist   | librarian | musician    | project-manager  | dressmaker | social-worker | lawyer |

