.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: jazz, folk, hip-hop, country, blues, electronic, rock
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, handball, parkour, sailing, snowboarding, soccer
House: gothic-revival, townhouse, art-deco, tower, cape-cod, craftsman, palace
 1. the fan of folk is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is the fan of rock##1
 6. the fan of jazz is the tower house##1
 7. the fan of jazz is between the person who's sport is soccer and the palace house##2
 8. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
10. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
11. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
12. the gothic-revival house is the fan of folk##1
13. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
14. the fan of country is on the right of the craftsman house##1
15. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | rock      | country     | jazz  | blues | hip-hop | folk |
| Sport         | cricket  | badminton | snowboarding | handball | soccer | parkour   | sailing  |
| House     | art-deco   | craftsman     | palace        | tower  | cape-cod   | townhouse       | gothic-revival      |

