.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, iced-tea, milk, soy-milk, tea, water
7 different pets are kept: cat, guinea-pig, frog, hedgehog, mouse, rabbit, pony
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, daisy, sunflower, rose, daffodil, azalea, zinnia
 1. the person who growsdaisy is the owner of the cat##1
 2. the person who growsdaffodil is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 3. the person who growsrose is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 4. the person who growssunflower is the person drinking fanta##1
 5. the person who growsazalea is between the person who growszinnia and the owner of the pony##2
 6. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 9. the person who growszinnia is on the far right##1
10. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
11. the person who growsdaisy is the owner of the cat##1
12. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
13. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
14. the person who growszinnia is the person drinking water##1
15. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |    6     |    7     |
| Beverage    | coffee     | soy-milk   | tea        | fanta   | iced-tea     | milk     | water    |
| Pet         | guinea-pig    | hedgehog | cat | mouse | pony | rabbit | frog |
| Flower   | amaryllis | daffodil       | daisy     | sunflower | rose   | azalea    | zinnia      |

