 2. the person who growsorchid is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 3. the french is the person who growsaconite##1
 4. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1
 5. the american is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's sport is baseball is in the middle##1
 8. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 9. the mexican is the person who growsazalea##1
10. the american is the person who's sport is swimming##1
11. the person who growspoppy is the turkish##1
12. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the italian##1
13. the indian is on the far right##1
14. the person who growsdahlia is between the person who growspoppy and the person who growsaconite##2
15. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1

