.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-5::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  analyst, architect, doctor, firefighter, freelancer, journalist, writer
City: prague, new-york, miami, hannover, marseilles, venice, rome
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, baccarat, bluemaster, cain, blend, prince, pall-mall
 1. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the writer##1
 2. the freelancer is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
 3. the freelancer is the person traveling to new-york##1
 4. the firefighter is the cain-smoker##1
 5. the blend-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 6. the person traveling to prague is the journalist##1
 7. the analyst is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 8. the baccarat-smoker is the doctor##1
 9. the game-smoker is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
10. the prince-smoker is the person traveling to prague##1
11. the doctor is on the right of the firefighter##1
12. the blend-smoker is between the doctor and the analyst##2
13. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the doctor##1
14. the game-smoker is the person traveling to marseilles##1
15. the freelancer is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
16. the cain-smoker is the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |     5      |     6      |     7     |
| Job           | firefighter | doctor    | writer    | analyst  | freelancer | journalist | architect |
| City   | hannover      | rome | miami | venice | new-york    | prague | marseilles    |
| Cigar     | cain     | baccarat      | blend    | pall-mall    | bluemaster  | prince       | game  |

