There are 7 different favourite colors: amber, light-blue, brown, green, ebony, red, azure
 1. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the security-guard##1
 2. the security-guard is on the left of the social-worker##1
 3. the person who likes green is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 4. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the chef##1
 5. the librarian is the person who likes ebony##1
 6. the person who likes amber is between the dancer and the social-worker##2
 7. the chef is in the middle##1
 8. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person who likes red##1
 9. the person who likes red is the person traveling to hamburg##1
10. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
11. the analyst is the person who likes brown##1
12. the analyst is the person who likes brown##1
13. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the chef##1
14. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
15. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |   4    |      5      |       6        |       7       |
| City   | hamburg       | edinburgh     | boston | marseilles  | paris | colone       | venice           |
