 3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
 4. the person who likes coral is between the person who likes emerald and the person who likes yellow##2
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 6. the person who likes chestnut is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 7. the person who likes emerald is the siglo-smoker##1
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 9. the person who likes purple is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
10. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
12. the person who's hobby is camping is in the middle##1
13. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
14. the montecristo-smoker is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
15. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
